Scope of this license — game content and trademarks

The MIT license above covers only the original source code and documentation
in this repository. It does NOT cover, and grants no rights whatsoever in,
Jeopardy! clue text, answers, category titles, or any other game content —
whether embedded in built artifacts in this repository (including the
published map page under docs/), produced by running the pipeline, or
obtained from upstream datasets. All such material remains the property of
its owners, including Jeopardy Productions, Inc.

JEOPARDY! is a registered trademark of Jeopardy Productions, Inc. This is an
unofficial fan and research project for noncommercial analysis and
commentary. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Jeopardy
Productions, Inc., Sony Pictures Television, or the Jeopardy! program.

Game content reaches this project through community-maintained datasets
derived from fan transcriptions. If you are a rights holder and would like
content removed, please open an issue or contact the repository owner, and it
will be taken down promptly.
